title: 1BR and 1Bath condo/Apartment available for rent in southwest
posting_body: ['Lovely Top Floor Unit!', 'Engineered Hardwood Floors throughout!', 'Maple Cabinets in Kitchen w/Custom Backsplash.', 'Built-in Table.', 'Living Room offers a Built-in Desk.', 'Bedroom offers a Walk-In Closet and Ceiling Fan.', 'Laundry Room in Unit offering great storage.', 'Unit also includes a Front Closet, Linen Closet and Storage Unit is just around the corner from the Unit!', 'Comes with the storage unit and assigned garage space in underground parking area.', 'New A/c and furnace unit.', 'Upgraded washer and dryer and new wooden floor  throughout.', 'Enjoy the Amenities Southwest Station offers such as Basketball Court, Exercise Room, Party Room, Patio and Outdoor Grill Area.', 'Southwest Station is close to transit station, future light rail station, shopping and restaurants as well as Highway Access to Downtown & the Airport.', 'Eden', 'Prairie offers great biking trails, walking trails and is known for exceptional parks!', '**Non-smoking', '**No pets', '**Have to pay one month advance rent as security.', '**Tenant insurance is mandatory.', '**Minimum 12 months rental duration/agreement is required.']
